reviewText: Outstanding look at the wonders of the cell: God as Creator, Master Designer.  Dr. Purdom is intellectually honest, scientifically accurate, and well-researched.

This video is more educational than entertaining. It details the amazing complexity in the world of the cell, the efficiency of systems that are at work within. I liked it a lot. Very thought-provoking!

This presentation is definitely not for kids or students, the product description is misleading. A person giving lecture on cells and other organs in the body mixing the god along with that, she failed both in explaining the Cell and also God.

Stay away stay away stay away
